question: Which movies were released in 2003?
typeql:
match $m isa movie, has released 2003, has title $t;
fetch { "title": $t };

question: List all movies with more than 1000 votes.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.votes > 1000
RETURN m.title, m.votes
typeql:
match $m isa movie, has votes $v, has title $t; $v > 1000;
fetch { "title": $t, "votes": $v };

question: What are the top 5 highest rated movies based on votes?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.votes IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title, m.votes
ORDER BY m.votes DESC
LIMIT 5

question: Find the first 3 people born after 1960.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
WHERE p.born > 1960
RETURN p
LIMIT 3

question: Who reviewed movies with a rating higher than 90?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[r:REVIEWED]->(m:Movie)
WHERE r.rating > 90
RETURN p.name AS reviewer, m.title AS movie, r.rating AS rating

question: List all movies directed by people born before 1950 limited to top 5.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie)
WHERE p.born < 1950
RETURN m.title
ORDER BY m.title
LIMIT 5

question: What are the roles of Keanu Reeves in the movies he acted in?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person {name: 'Keanu Reeves'})-[r:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie)
RETURN m.title AS movie, r.roles AS roles

question: Find the first 3 movies produced by someone born in 1952.
Who acted in the movie with the tagline 'Welcome to the Real World'?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:ACTED_IN]->(m:Movie {tagline: 'Welcome to the Real World'})
RETURN p.name

question: Display the top 5 movies that have been reviewed with the summary 'Dark, but compelling'.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:REVIEWED]-(p:Person)
WHERE r.summary = 'Dark, but compelling'
RETURN m.title, r.rating
ORDER BY r.rating DESC
LIMIT 5

question: Show the top 3 movies with the lowest number of votes.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.votes
ORDER BY m.votes
LIMIT 3

question: Who are the first 3 people to follow Keanu Reeves?
List all people who have produced a movie and acted in another.
What are the top 5 most recent movies in the database?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.released
ORDER BY m.released DESC
LIMIT 5

question: Find all movies with a released year in the 1990s.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.released >= 1990 AND m.released < 2000
RETURN m

question: Who wrote the movie titled 'The Matrix'?
List the first 3 people born in 1964.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
WHERE p.born = 1964
RETURN p.name
LIMIT 3

question: Which movies have been reviewed with a rating less than 50?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:REVIEWED]-(p:Person)
WHERE r.rating < 50
RETURN m.title, r.rating, r.summary
